name: Pika Pika
description:
Sylvie's Mystery Shop Day 4:
Today we had a funeral in shop, penguins were really sad and still couldn't find the impostor.
And also cat wanted to be the priest... 

Ash and Pikachu came to my shop, ı was so excited Pikachu was so cute, Ash said "pikachu loves ketchup" ı guess pika pika means ı love ketchup ı'm still not sure but anyway ı sold them a ketchup and a pokeball.
